            "creation_date": 1490245760,
            "body": "<p>Have you tried by passing Object class or by passing generic type reference?<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public String updateRecord(@RequestBody Object obj,..\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>or<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public String updateRecord(@RequestBody T obj,.. // I am not sure for this\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Then check <code>instanceOf<\/code> in your controller method.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 42967679,
